CLI Parameters (Python)

--plant {first,second}    Plant type
--tau FLOAT               Time constant for first-order (default 1.0)
--wn FLOAT                Natural frequency for second-order (default 2.0)
--zeta FLOAT              Damping ratio for second-order (default 0.3)
--kp FLOAT                Proportional gain (default 1.0)
--ki FLOAT                Integral gain (default 0.0)
--kd FLOAT                Derivative gain (default 0.0)
--tend FLOAT              Simulation end time (default 10.0)
--noise FLOAT             Measurement noise std dev (default 0.0)
--dt FLOAT                Time step for fallback integrator (default 0.001)
